APX Group Holdings, Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 10 17
APX Group Holdings, Inc. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, the company reported total revenues of $205,353,000 against $174,253,000 a year ago. Loss from operations was $16,527,000 against $3,675,000 a year ago. Loss before income taxes was $82,217,000 against $43,973,000 a year ago. Net loss was $82,636,000 against $45,093,000 a year ago. Net cash used in operating activities was $6,153,000 against $12,505,000 a year ago. Adjusted EBITDA was $115.4 million against $102.8 million a year ago.


