Company Overview of APX Group, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
APX Group, Inc. offers residential security solutions and home automation services. It provides interactive security, life-safety, energy management, and home automation products and services. The company was founded in 2012 and is based in Provo, Utah. APX Group, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of APX Group Holdings, Inc.


