following the call.


About Vivint


As a leading smart home technology provider, Vivint offers home security, energy management, home automation, local cloud storage, and high-speed Internet solutions to more than 900,000 customers throughout
the United States
,
Canada
and
New Zealand
. The end-result is a smart home solution that saves you time and money and ultimately simplifies your life. For more information, visit the Company’s website at
www.vivint.com
.


